{"tid":383306,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國歌法魔鬼在細節 學好普通話先？","createTime":"2017-09-01T11:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T14:27:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffcd3e73fa1b017aacfbb807c0db4d6fc0f24190","tid":383306,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:08:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20139501&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20139501%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170901&d=Od297faog6gO%2BNk5sSXTT6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=cf266d66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20139501%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170901&h=5aa4fab8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20139501&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170901</a><br />\n<br />\n國歌法魔鬼在細節<br />\n學好普通話先？<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委計劃將《國歌法》納入全國性法律，並適用於港澳地區。身兼港區人大代表的立法會議員田北辰在電台節目中一再指國歌法「魔鬼在細節」當中，認為唱國歌時不專心、普通話發音有問題，都不等於不尊重國歌，質疑政府到時如何執法，類似的細節應事前釐清。<br />\n<br />\n田以看球賽舉例，稱在球賽開始前播國歌，但球迷分心只留意球星、無一起唱國歌或普通話發音有問題，當局是否要派出大量執法人員到場，以及如可演繹「不尊重」的意思，他認為政府應在實施前先解釋清楚。<br />\n<br />\n他稱由於《國家法》將透過《基本法》附件三引入香港成為本地法例，立法會在審議時應討論受規範的行為和法例字眼，希望討論能聚焦在「莊重、尊重」等字眼。"},{"pid":"c29997f7ee72e93ae5317783d4a0c102bf8e9217","tid":383306,"uid":125978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20139501&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170901\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20139501%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170901&d=Od297faog6gO%2BNk5sSXTT6EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=cf266d66\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20139501%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170901&h=5aa4fab8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20139501&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170901</a><br />\n<br />\n國歌法魔鬼在細節<br />\n學好普通話先？<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委計劃將《國歌法》納入全國性法律，並適用於港澳地區。身兼港區人大代表的立法會議員田北辰在電台節目中一再指國歌法「魔鬼在細節」當中，認為唱國歌時不專心、普通話發音有問題，都不等於不尊重國歌，質疑政府到時如何執法，類似的細節應事前釐清。<br />\n<br />\n田以看球賽舉例，稱在球賽開始前播國歌，但球迷分心只留意球星、無一起唱國歌或普通話發音有問題，當局是否要派出大量執法人員到場，以及如可演繹「不尊重」的意思，他認為政府應在實施前先解釋清楚。<br />\n<br />\n他稱由於《國家法》將透過《基本法》附件三引入香港成為本地法例，立法會在審議時應討論受規範的行為和法例字眼，希望討論能聚焦在「莊重、尊重」等字眼。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵我？"},{"pid":"1a61c5be5dc9121589822774b2d47ec8e2c75cb9","tid":383306,"uid":86943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"每次噤沖水掣會播國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c0347e5a92e16fa92c6e8a20b5c47cca160dc7f","tid":383306,"uid":83927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"唔唱咪唔會錯囉"},{"pid":"812c9258376d29f438d258839e092ac74141d3c9","tid":383306,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T11:26:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔唱咪唔會錯囉</blockquote><br />\n你唔唱 係到按電話都拉得"},{"pid":"e6b1e538019cfdcd7175b3073ae555246445428e","tid":383306,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔唱咪唔會錯囉</blockquote><br />\n你唔唱 係到按電話都拉得</blockquote><br />\n三個人出街都拉得"},{"pid":"5ba858a488990a827b2e96b5acd911bc857b3c4c","tid":383306,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:36:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔唱咪唔會錯囉</blockquote><br />\n當然，否則非華裔人士可能被拉（因為唔識華語）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi